10-facts-about-cubans-in-the-u-s/</guid></item><item><title>妈妈、教练、医生、企业家：谁是美国健康和保健的影响者？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/data-labs/2026/05/07/moms-coaches-doctors-entrepreneurs-who-are-americas-health-and-wellness-influencers/</link><description>一半 50 岁以下的美国成年人表示，他们从社交媒体影响者或播客中获取健康和保健信息。这些影响者中约有十分之四的人将自己描述为医疗保健专业人员；教练和企业家几乎同样常见。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/data-labs/2026/05/07/moms-coaches-doctors-entrepreneurs-who-are-americas-health-and-wellness-influencers/</guid></item><item><title>71% 的美国房主表示他们的房屋保险费用上涨</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/06/71-of-u-s-homeowners-say-their-home-insurance-costs-have-gone-up/</link><description>房主最常提到的两个原因是保险公司想要赚更多钱以及维修和重建的成本。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/06/71-of-u-s-homeowners-say-their-home-insurance-costs-have-gone-up/</guid></item></channel></rss>